      "content": "interesting. it seems like you're leaning pretty heavily on certain racial traits to signal these personality types. why do you think those specific ethnicities are the ones that most effectively communicate those roles to an audience? is there a specific reason why a character from a different background wouldn't work for those same archetypes?",
